structure.unit: Chapter 33J FIRE AND EMERGENCY MEDICAL SERVICES IMPACT FEE

text.section:
Sec. 33J-1. Short title and applicability.
This chapter [Ordinance Number 90-26] shall be known and may be cited as the "Miami-Dade County Fire and Emergency Medical Services Impact Fee Ordinance."
This chapter shall be applicable to land development throughout the district including unincorporated Miami-Dade County and all municipalities served by the district.
